### **1 / 71492 Jupiter DAO Tokens**

This token represents proportional ownership over Jupiter. Together with other Jupiter DAO Token holders, its owner is able to actively build and govern the planet into its own unique environment.

*Jupiter represents 10.4% of the total voting power for MetaHero Universe's United Planets DAO.*
